name: "richie es un punk rocker"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
very pleased to introduce Ricardus #20, the punky one, a very special person who spends 24/7 listening to the Ramones and talking about anarchy.
he's really cute at heart but you wouldn't want to cross him at a punk demonstration. is he a real punk or is he the original Ricardus dressed up for Halloween?
